Use Case: Request Directory
Context: At any time, a provider can request the software product for a Provider Directory.
Actors: Provider

Main Success Scenario:
	1. A provider uses their ChocAn computer terminal to request the ChocAn Data Center to send them a Provider Directory.
	2. The ChocAn Data Center receives the request and sends the Provider Directory to the provider as an e-mail attachment.

Extensions:
	1a. An invalid provider number was entered.
		1a.1. The ChocAn computer terminal informs the provider. 
		1a.2. The use case continues at step 1.